OL,3,CHaboobs and 'blood rain': Britain's
OL,4,Cskies to ignite with intense, fiery
OL,5,Csunsets
OL,7,FIf you've been lucky enough to catch a
OL,8,Fclear evening sky lately, you've
OL,9,Fprobably noticed just how breathtaking
OL,10,Fthe sunsets have been.
OL,12,FBut why are they happening? How long
OL,13,Fwill they last? And what is the so-
OL,14,Fcalled 'blood rain' we're
OL,15,Fexperiencing? Here's everything you
OL,16,Fneed to know:
OL,18,FWhy are the sunsets suddenly so vivid?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
