OL,3,CHaboobs and 'blood rain': Britain's
OL,4,Cskies to ignite with intense, fiery
OL,5,Csunsets
OL,7,FIn a word: Dust. A plume of very fine
OL,8,Fsand and mineral particles has
OL,9,Ftravelled all the way from North
OL,10,FAfrica to the UK on warm southerly
OL,11,Fwinds.
OL,13,FThose dust particles are now swirling
OL,14,Faround high up in our atmosphere. As
OL,15,Fthe sun rises and sets, its light must
OL,16,Ftravel through a greater portion of
OL,17,Fthe atmosphere.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772730673
OL,3,CHaboobs and 'blood rain': Britain's
OL,4,Cskies to ignite with intense, fiery
OL,5,Csunsets
OL,7,FThe tiny dust particles scatter away
OL,8,Fthe shorter blue tones, and allow
OL,9,Fthose richer reds, ambers and burnt
OL,10,Foranges to shine through.
OL,12,FThat's why the sky can look almost
OL,13,Fglowing ` especially when conditions
OL,14,Fare clear and calm.
OL,16,FHow has that desert dust reached so
OL,17,Ffar northwards - and what on earth is
OL,18,Fa 'haboob'?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
