OL,3,CHaboobs and 'blood rain': Britain's
OL,4,Cskies to ignite with intense, fiery
OL,5,Csunsets
OL,7,FNow, with high pressure bringing
OL,8,Fsettled, mild weather to the UK, that
OL,9,Fdusty air is being steered our way.
OL,11,FHow unusual is it?
OL,13,FIt happens more often than you might
OL,14,Fthink - we see this phenomenon several
OL,15,Ftimes a year, particularly in late
OL,16,Fwinter and spring. Even though the
OL,17,Fresults can look astounding.
OL,19,FAnd what about 'blood rain'?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
