PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772730673
OL,3,CHaboobs and 'blood rain': Britain's
OL,4,Cskies to ignite with intense, fiery
OL,5,Csunsets
OL,7,FIt sounds alarming, but it's harmless!
OL,8,FIf rain falls while the dust is
OL,9,Foverhead, the tiny particles get
OL,10,Ftrapped in raindrops and fall to the
OL,11,Fground.
OL,13,FThis can leave a thin reddish-brown
OL,14,Fcoating on cars, windows and garden
OL,15,Ffurniture.
OL,17,FIt's known as "blood rain" because of
OL,18,Fthe rusty colour - but it's simply
OL,19,Frainwater mixed with desert dust.
OL,21,FWhen will skies look their best?
OL,26,@yD@OOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
